Change the background color of the navigation.

Open _sass/_navigation.scss, modify the color:

```
.greedy-nav {
  position: relative;
  min-width: 250px;
  background:  rgba(169,190,123,0.8); //rgba(46,89,167,0.8);  // $background-color;
  ....

```
